{"type": "article", "id": 21742, "title": "柏林这家酒店，请你挑选 100 多个完全不一样的房间", "description": "你可以在6种类型里选，完全是年轻人会好奇的样子。", "date": "2016-02-02T19:00:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 667, "name": "酒店"}, {"id": 4083, "name": "柏林"}, {"id": 12317, "name": "年轻化"}, {"id": 23037, "name": "Michelberger"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 495, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702172323maoWgZvspyTOENwL.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>年轻人喜欢什么样的酒店？</p>\n<p>近几年流行的青旅也许是其中一个风格，距离市中心近，有好的沟通环境，即使环境嘈杂生活条件差一点也无所谓。但越来越多的酒店开始注重设计，比如柏林Michelberger，它在<a href=\"http://www.top10berlin.de/en/cat/hotels-2485/design-and-boutique-hotels-2509/michelberger-hotel-3160#1\"> top 10 berlin</a> 网上被评选为10个最具设计和时尚感的酒店（Design and Boutique Hotels）之一，据说 119 间房间都不一样。</p>\n<p>这家酒店开于 2009 年 9 月，由几个年轻人一起经营，他们并不想照搬精品酒店的样子，而是向往一种创意和叛逆的风格。Michelberger 是从一个大的工厂放改造的，每层的层高很高，拥有砖墙和大窗户。这样的条件很容易将房间改成 loft，但他们还是将酒店的房间划分为 6 种类型，舒适、阁楼、奢华、藏身处、乐队和大房间，并联合设计师改造。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>阁楼（Loft）</p>\n<p>层高最高的房间就做成了 loft，柏林的设计师 Werner Aisslinger 曾参与改建了其中的房子，他们使用了低价的材料，想让它成为一间招揽朋友来聚会的卧室。</p>\n<p class=\"\">房间的摆放的物件很多是客人自己制作或者留下来的，设计师刻意去找手工艺者做了一些有手工感的东西，让房间体现出熟悉自然。二楼的床铺用网格做围栏，人多的时候，可以住到 4 个人。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172309eKSXEtNnzaWqs5QR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172309zFvm3nc597B1NKjP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172310ObEIoVP5DgrS0Gu8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172310lsz6wgCm4r9GpdZK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70879121\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>藏身处（Hideout）</p>\n<p>丹麦建筑师 Sigurd Larsen 改造的属于藏身处的 304 号房间，他在大房间里加了一个小木屋。想要让木盒子像一个家，外面像一个花园。</p>\n<p class=\"\">盒子的一楼有桑拿房、卫生间、厨房和卧室。二楼有另一个卧室，沙发，餐厅等公共区域都在外面的“花园里”，小房间显得格外温馨。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172311b1EjXGNVQSZrat7f.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172312GEXBF51jJ0PQmC4i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6741453\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172312ZhCOcuvy5HLzYUQF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172313F1MYyflbs60m9ETr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172313Gs068eSZdo9JqBh7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172314dgG7EhZoI9S5KpX1.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172314ONocwb1v029urznl.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>舒适（Cosy）</p>\n<p>舒适类房间是单人间，面积最小，有一张大床。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172315Ux7KbsE2l6gcNrnS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>乐队（Band）</p>\n<p>乐队房适合家庭单位的团队，能住 3 到  4个人。上下分别能铺两张床。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172315jZLEu1xld76msbCN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172316mIrXyHES2eiMWhjL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172316c9OhAmgvsGNktleb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>大房间（The Big One）</p>\n<p>大房间有 6 张单人床，它更接近青年旅舍。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172317ghwbeBdXoniYmaUt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172317g6uToU3QNM41r2cH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172318oSWZCHn2UwvqEfgN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>奢华（Luxus）</p>\n<p>酒店一共只有 4 间奢华房，有舒适型的小屋，金色的华丽的房间，充满书本的古典风格的房间和操场风格。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172319DrohlfvNL42Eke1C.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172319oY6QjA39gcFVrf2P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172320W0iaNlbQBZ2zwMkh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172320kjFZe6XyRSL5wpbl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172321KCwpVlEL9JkQ8BFD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021723215I8lJmdcLeayVU1M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021723220OpDNaHstxJPQko2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>Michelberger 酒店在 Friedrichshain 区，对面就是城市轻轨和地铁站，距离柏林墙 East Side Gallery 一段只有 5 分钟的路程。经营者希望这里成为年轻人的聚集地。</p>\n<p>这是酒店的<a href=\"http://michelbergerhotel.com/en/\">订阅页面</a>，一个漂浮在黑色夜空的移动城堡。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172322SaiysI4wB7HOmdDN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/01/30/the-garden-room-michelberger-hotel-room-playhouse-sigurd-larsen-berlin-germany/\"> dezeen</a>、<a href=\"http://michelbergerhotel.com/en/\">Michelberger</a></p>\n<p>          </p>\n\n\n"}